<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ل ث م<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٤٥٢٨ - ل ث م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لثِمَ يَلثَم، لَثْمًا، فهو لاثم، والمفعول مَلثوم <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• لثِمت المرأةُ:</span> شدّت الِّلثَام على أنفها.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• لثِم فاها:</span> لثَمه؛ قبَّله <span class="c1">"لثِم رأسَه"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>